history.content:
I am helping to conduct a user study on interactions with spreadsheets — it will be a series of web-based tasks to analyze a data set using the tool provided. The study is remote, and it will take around an hour. You will be compensated $10 in cash.  We are affiliated with Professor Aditya parameswaran and berkeley rise lab 
If you are interested, you can sign up with this link below. If you have any questions, you can contact me via nathanzhang1@berkeley.edu

Signup link: https://www.wejoinin.com/sheets/cdsmu
history.subject: User study on interactive spreadsheets affiliated with Riselabs
